  "title": "The impact of origin region and internal migration on Italian fertility",
  "abstract": "We examine the impact of population distribution on fertility in a nationally representative sample. We exploit detailed life-history data to conduct an event-history analysis of transition to first birth, examining mechanisms that might link migration",
